blog.name: friendsafariserver
blog.title: Friend Safari!
blog.description:
Friend Safari is a SFW, OC-friendly, paragraph-style roleplay server for main series Pokémon games. From Kanto to Alola, the whole Pokémon world is your Cloyster! Members of this server are allowed a total of four played characters, with at least one required to be canonical.

The server is run by a team of five mods who you can learn more about via the mods page. We cultivate an easygoing and open atmosphere, with member comfort and happiness being our top priority.

All of the links are in the drop down menu under Rowlet, labeled Pokémon! Hovering over each Pokémon will tell you what page they link to!

title: Exploud - 295
body:
Exploud triggers earthquakes with the tremors it creates by bellowing. If this Pokemon violently inhales from the ports on its body, it’s a sign that it is preparing to let loose a huge bellow.

Basically I just wanna like... Change the shinies I don't...
body:
Hey guys! I'mma try and fix bad shiny pokemon, give me suggestions!

Basically I just wanna like… Change the shinies I don’t like or that I think are boring, it’ll take me a while and I doubt I’ll even complete the list I have rn, but I’m open for more suggestions!

Here is my current list;

- Gengar (to be remade)

- Garchomp (to be remade)

- Squirtle

- Metapod and Butterfree

- Weedle (fixed)

- Nidoqueen

- Espeon (fixed)

- Meowth and Persian

- Dragonite (fixed)

Edit;

- Leafeon (to be remade)
